<div class="flex flex-col items-start bg-gray-8 relative flex-1 justify-between ">
    <div class="bg-cover bg-bottom bg-no-repeat w-full pt-6 px-5 pb-12" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path 'background_design.svg' %>)">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-6">
            <% if current_user&.profile&.image&.attached? %>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative w-12 h-12 rounded-full">
                    <%= image_tag url_for(current_user.profile.image), class: "rounded-full absolute" %>
                </div>
            <% else %>
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-300 p-5 flex flex-row items-center justify-center">
                    <%= image_tag url_for("user_avatar.svg") %>
                </div>
            <% end %>
            
           <div class="w-full flex flex-row items-center justify-between grow ml-5 ">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <p class="text-lg italic font-black text-red">Melia Antiqua</p>
                    <p class="font-normal text-sm">CTO, Bionis, Inc.</p>
                </div>
                <%= inline_svg_tag "circle_with_checkmark.svg", class: "fill-red-500" %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-xl text-red-500 mb-4 font-bold mb-4">Level up performance with simple coding changes</h1>

        <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 mb-[18px]">
            <div class="bg-white border border-blue-2 rounded-lg px-4 py-[6px] text-blue-2">
                Front-end
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-blue-2 rounded-lg px-4 py-[6px] text-blue-2">
                Tailwind
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-blue-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-[6px] text-blue-2">
                CSS
            </div>
        </div>
       
        <p class="font-normal mb-6 leading-6 text-base">This presentation will first highlight some
        of the major improvements Bionis, Inc. has achieved using straightforward
        Ruby techniques and her approach to solving technical problems centers
        around ensuring the continued stability and extensibility for individual
        developers and companies large and small.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-1">
            <%= inline_svg_tag "calendar.svg", class: "fill-gray-4 w-3 h-3 mr-2" %> <p class="text-[13px]">Thursday, Sept 26 </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-1">
            <%= inline_svg_tag "clock.svg", class: "stroke-gray-4 w-3 h-3 mr-2" %><p class="text-[13px]">09:00 - 12:00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-1">
            <%= inline_svg_tag "location_pin.svg", class: "stroke-gray-4 w-3 h-3 mr-2" %><p class="text-[13px]">Conference Hall</p>
        </div>

        
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-5">
        <p class="text-black mb-4 text-2xl font-bold italic">About this speaker</p>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg bg-white">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-6">
                <% if current_user&.profile&.image&.attached? %>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative w-12 h-12 rounded-full">
                        <%= image_tag url_for(current_user.profile.image), class: "rounded-full absolute" %>
                    </div>
                <% else %>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-300 p-5 flex flex-row items-center justify-center">
                        <%= image_tag url_for("user_avatar.svg") %>
                    </div>
                <% end %>
                <div class="flex flex-col ml-5">
                    <p class="text-lg italic font-black text-red">Melia Antiqua</p>
                    <p class="font-normal text-sm">CTO, Bionis, Inc.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>
            Melia is on the Ruby core team and is the Chief Technology Officer at Bionis, Inc. In her free time, she enjoys gardening, swimming, and socialising.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
